00:10.024 --> 00:11.947
We have to remember that.

00:12.471 --> 00:13.728
Shit.

00:13.799 --> 00:14.610
It's actually happened,

00:14.611 --> 00:16.722
I'm talking to an imaginary person.

00:18.399 --> 00:19.600
