00:24.599 --> 00:26.562
There's a powerful
group of people out there

00:26.563 --> 00:28.602
that are secretly running the world.

00:30.299 --> 00:32.234
I'm talking about the
guys no one knows about,

00:32.235 --> 00:34.082
the guys that are invisible.

00:35.199 --> 00:38.419
The top 1% of the top
1%, the guys that play God

00:38.420 --> 00:40.236
