00:58.499 --> 01:00.699
Instead, I went to...

01:13.299 --> 01:14.049
Hey, Ron.

01:14.050 --> 01:15.503
There you go.

01:51.699 --> 01:53.699
You're Ron.

01:57.618 --> 02:00.936
But your real name is Rohit Mehta.

02:00.937 --> 02:02.719
You changed it to Ron when you bought

02:02.720 --> 02:04.224
your first Ron's Coffee Shop

02:04.225 --> 02:05.906
six years ago.

02:05.999 --> 02:09.745
Now you got 17 of 'em with
8 more coming next quarter.

02:12.763 --> 02:14.566
May I help you with something?

02:14.700 --> 02:18.002
I like coming here 'cause
your Wi-Fi was fast.

02:18.003 --> 02:19.141
I mean, you're one of the few spots

02:19.142 --> 02:21.911
that has a fiber connection
with gigabit speed.

02:21.912 --> 02:23.213
It's good.

02:23.670 --> 02:27.177
So good, it scratched
that part of my mind, part

02:27.178 --> 02:30.938
that doesn't allow good
to exist without condition,

02:30.939 --> 02:33.602
so I started intercepting all the traffic

02:33.603 --> 02:34.872
on your network.

02:34.899 --> 02:37.160
That's when I noticed something strange.

02:38.212 --> 02:40.915
It's when I decided to hack you.

02:41.899 --> 02:43.683
- Hack...
- I know you run a website

02:43.684 --> 02:46.213
- called Plato's Boys.
- Pardon me?

02:46.214 --> 02:48.899
You're using Tor networking
to keep the servers anonymous.

02:48.900 --> 02:49.950
You made it really hard

02:49.951 --> 02:52.708
for anyone to see it, but I saw it.

02:53.181 --> 02:54.617
The onion routing protocol,

02:54.618 --> 02:56.899
it's not as anonymous as you think it is.

02:56.900 --> 02:58.899
Whoever's in control of the exit nodes

02:58.900 --> 03:00.899
is also in control of the traffic,

03:00.900 --> 03:02.677
which makes me...

03:03.344 --> 03:04.899
the one in control.

03:06.899 --> 03:08.899
I must ask you to kindly leave.

03:08.900 --> 03:11.834
I own everything. All your emails.

03:11.835 --> 03:13.398
All your files.

03:13.399 --> 03:14.899
All your... pics.

03:18.099 --> 03:20.240
Get out of here right now,

03:20.241 --> 03:22.054
- or I'll call the...
- Police?

03:22.055 --> 03:23.098
You want them to find out

03:23.099 --> 03:25.339
about the 100 terabytes
of child pornography

03:25.340 --> 03:27.691
you serve to your 400,000 users?

03:28.799 --> 03:31.017
Personally, man, I was

03:31.018 --> 03:32.700
hoping it was just gonna be

03:32.701 --> 03:34.524
some BDSM stuff.

03:35.013 --> 03:37.787
You realize how much
simpler that would have been?

03:42.199 --> 03:45.199
I did not hurt anyone.

03:45.200 --> 03:47.199
I never did.

03:52.899 --> 03:54.034
That's my...

03:54.035 --> 03:55.597
personal life.

03:59.699 --> 04:02.779
I understand what it's like

04:02.780 --> 04:04.829
to be different.

04:06.699 --> 04:09.607
I'm very different too.

04:11.299 --> 04:14.412
I mean, I don't jerk off
to little kids, but...

04:16.099 --> 04:18.149
I don't know how to talk to people.

04:18.798 --> 04:21.798
My dad was the only one I could talk to.

04:24.499 --> 04:26.499
But he died.

04:31.499 --> 04:33.360
I'm sorry to hear that.

04:35.200 --> 04:39.138
- How did he pass, may I ask?
- Leukemia.

04:40.399 --> 04:43.985
He definitely got it from
radiation at the company

04:43.986 --> 04:46.233
