04:47.399 --> 04:48.659
Now he's dead.

04:49.999 --> 04:52.000
Company's fine, though.

04:55.199 --> 04:57.870
Oh... hey.

04:59.799 --> 05:01.799
It's okay, Rohit.

05:02.799 --> 05:05.067
You don't have to worry anymore.

05:06.999 --> 05:08.999
I don't understand.

05:09.899 --> 05:11.900
Are you blackmailing me?

05:13.300 --> 05:15.678
So that's what this is about...

05:15.679 --> 05:17.600
money.

05:17.601 --> 05:20.737
That's all you care about, huh?

05:21.399 --> 05:23.399
No.

05:24.799 --> 05:26.266
If I pay you now,

05:26.267 --> 05:28.173
