05:28.174 --> 05:30.426
No matter how much I give.

05:32.268 --> 05:34.799
You will inform the police anyway.

05:34.800 --> 05:36.799
I won't pay you, sir.

05:38.799 --> 05:41.139
Remember, you also broke the law.

05:43.099 --> 05:45.099
Actually, you're right.

05:45.100 --> 05:46.909
Partly.

05:47.816 --> 05:50.682
See, I usually do this kind
of thing from my computer,

05:50.683 --> 05:52.878
but this time I wanted to do it AFK.

05:53.799 --> 05:55.799
In person.

05:55.800 --> 05:58.061
Trying to work on my social anxiety.

05:58.599 --> 06:00.434
But there's always the
threat of you fleeing

06:00.435 --> 06:01.810
after I call you out.

06:01.811 --> 06:05.045
You'd tell your sys admin
to take your servers down,

06:05.046 --> 06:06.346
wipe all the data.

06:06.347 --> 06:09.838
So I made sure to include the current time

06:09.839 --> 06:13.088
and... and location on my anonymous tip.

06:13.089 --> 06:14.795
Wait. Hold on. I'll give you the money.

06:14.796 --> 06:15.848
I'll pay you.

06:15.849 --> 06:17.709
How much do you want? I'll pay you.

06:18.768 --> 06:21.255
That's the part you
were wrong about, Rohit.

06:21.779 --> 06:24.543
I don't give a shit about money.

06:36.834 --> 06:38.830
Now I'm being followed.

06:45.161 --> 06:47.168
The higher ups don't like
someone with my powers.

06:47.169 --> 06:49.862
In three short minutes, I
destroyed a man's business,

06:49.863 --> 06:51.337
life, existence.

06:51.685 --> 06:53.692
- I deleted him.
- Hey!

06:54.723 --> 06:57.367
Hey, you. Hey, kiddo.

06:58.606 --> 07:00.613
What's happening?

07:05.704 --> 07:08.083
Exciting time in the world right now.

07:09.040 --> 07:12.051
Exciting time.

07:33.412 --> 07:35.621
But I'm only a vigilante hacker by night.

07:35.622 --> 07:38.626
By day, just a regular
cyber security engineer,

07:39.345 --> 07:43.232
employee number ER28-0652.

07:45.068 --> 07:46.072
Elliot!

07:46.073 --> 07:49.081
In here.

07:52.092 --> 07:54.099
- What's up?
- El.

08:00.120 --> 08:02.672
All over the price...
Yeah, I can totally...

08:02.673 --> 08:03.979
I can totally handle it.

08:03.980 --> 08:05.986
