08:25.718 --> 08:28.215
Let's just see how this meeting goes today.

08:28.216 --> 08:30.818
Their networks are getting
attacked every week.

08:30.819 --> 08:33.232
Who knows if they'll
still even be a client.

08:34.448 --> 08:36.532
- They're coming in?
- Hey, what did we say

08:36.533 --> 08:39.763
