case they have any questions.

08:44.811 --> 08:48.085
- Okay?
- Okay.

08:51.110 --> 08:53.863
- Start smoking again?
- Did you not get my texts last night?

08:53.864 --> 08:56.223
I sent you exactly 13 of them.

08:56.224 --> 08:58.348
Yeah, I'm sorry. I couldn't make it.

09:01.329 --> 09:04.087
