09:24.255 --> 09:27.464
Sorry. I was thinking about work.

09:27.799 --> 09:29.799
Maybe that's why Gideon loves you so much.

09:29.800 --> 09:31.799
He thanks me all the
time for bringing you in.

09:31.800 --> 09:35.011
But for some reason, I think
you secretly hate it here.

09:35.799 --> 09:37.799
