10:23.075 --> 10:27.389
Angela, I can't have that
kind of negativity in my life.

10:28.399 --> 10:31.799
That's exactly what I'm talking about.

10:41.800 --> 10:43.799
What are you thinking about?

10:45.800 --> 10:46.799
