your anger issues, Elliot.

11:48.471 --> 11:51.199
You're angry at everyone, at society...

11:51.200 --> 11:52.161
Fuck society.

11:52.562 --> 11:54.299
I know you have a lot to be angry about,

11:54.300 --> 11:57.058
but keeping it to yourself and
staying quiet like you're doing...

11:57.108 --> 11:59.807
