12:00.401 --> 12:03.882
There's pain underneath. That's
where our work needs to go.

12:07.839 --> 12:11.855
What is it about society
that disappoints you so much?

12:18.255 --> 12:20.608
Oh, I don't know.

12:20.609 --> 12:23.481
Is it that we collectively
thought Steve Jobs

12:23.482 --> 12:25.432
was a great man, even when we knew

12:25.433 --> 12:29.850
