12:29.851 --> 12:34.027
Or maybe it's that it feels like
all our heroes are counterfeit.

12:34.272 --> 12:37.387
The world itself's just one big hoax.

12:38.190 --> 12:41.443
Spamming with our running
commentary of bullshit

12:41.444 --> 12:46.421
