12:51.111 --> 12:53.345
Not with our rigged
elections, but with our things,

12:53.346 --> 12:55.517
our property, our money.

12:55.518 --> 12:58.234
I'm not saying anything new.
We all know why we do this,

12:58.235 --> 13:00.791
not because Hunger Games
books makes us happy

13:01.176 --> 13:03.342
but because we wanna be sedated.

13:03.343 --> 13:05.352
